{
  "id": "adv_main_03_04_02",
  "title": "BIG4編1章17話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　{user}さんと\nさとみちゃんがデートしてる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! {user}-san and\nSatomi are on a date!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4045780094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha—!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.3100679795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや、その、私と{user}さんは\n別に、その～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no‚ it’s not like that‚ {user}-san and I\naren’t‚ you know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら、芽衣。俺達は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey hey‚ Mei. We’re…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.851247239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.448616274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "いいなー。{user}さん\n今度芽衣ともデートしようよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so jealous~. {user}-san‚\nlet's go on a date next time with Mei too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3152829407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……人の話を聞きなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Listen to what people are saying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.248616274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5461445012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、{user}さん？　どうして\n芽衣ちゃんからデートに誘われて動揺しないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ {user}-san? Why aren't you fazed\nby being asked out on a date by Mei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2666654586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5948520658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "あの芽衣ちゃんから！　デートに！\n誘われてるんですよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By Mei-chan! On a date!\nShe’s asking you out!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1333321253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんも落ち着いて？\nここ、事務所じゃないからな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hashimoto-san‚ please calm down.\nThis isn’t the office‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2288883766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.218321339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、芽衣とはよくデートしてるもんね？\nもう慣れっこだよねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Mei go on dates a lot with {user}-san‚ right?\nWe’re used to it by now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7680115856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、一緒にコンビニとかスーパーに\n行ってるだけだろう……沙季？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no‚ we’re just going to the convenience store or\nsupermarket together… Saki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6288883766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.6266887025
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.6266887025
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.8766887025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはやめて！\nホントに、ちょっ、ダメだったら……あっ、あーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Stop it!\nReally‚ just‚ if it doesn’t work… Ah‚ ahh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3100220359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.6766887025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あー……もぉ……\n……ねっ、もう一回っ、もう一回っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh… Ugh…\n…Hey‚ one more time‚ one more time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.86222171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "しかも芽衣ちゃんの方から……\nもう一回、しちゃうんだ。すごい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Mei-chan’s the one who…\nasks for another go. Amazing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8433553692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 67.8638765013
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.9805434224
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.9805434224
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.2305434224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "星見市にいた時の一件は冤罪に終わりましたが、私達が\n油断した頃に再び事を起こすとは……さすがですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While the incident back in Hoshimi City ended up being a false accusation‚\nto think you'd try it again when we're off guard… As expected of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3433553692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.2766978578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ゲス……いえ、{user}さん\n後でお話があります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You scumba… I mean‚ {user}-san‚\nwe need to talk later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7433553692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.6433645245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ沙季、今回も冤罪だからな！？\nそもそも、俺と橋本さんはデートしてる訳じゃないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute‚ Saki‚ you got me wrokng this time too!?\nTo begin with‚ Hashimoto-san and I aren’t on a date!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2985351647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私だってもう子供じゃありませんから\nそれくらい分かりますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not a child anymore‚\nso I know that much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3986973463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4198513504
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.9198421951
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "この状況は……なるほど\nさとみさんとは遊びという訳ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This situation is… I see.\nYou're just playing around with Satomi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9198421951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "解釈が悪化してるぞ！？　まったく……沙季は\n渚に借りた恋愛小説の影響を受け過ぎじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your interpretation is getting worse!? Geez… Saki‚\nyou've read too many of romance novels you borrowed from Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0955565692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.080814838
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 121.5141481713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん\n失礼しました、少々からかい過ぎましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ahem.\nI apologize‚ I teased you a bit too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5141481713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.5141507144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_04_02-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "私達は最近ずっと、どりきゅんの情報を集めてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been gathering information on DoriKyun lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5141507144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.3525635555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
